data.description: Welcome home! 1212 Big Bend Rd is a cozy and comfortable home that has been well taken care of since its many recent updates in 2022. The property offers lots of natural sunlight, main level laundry, and gorgeous tray ceilings in the living room, main level bedroom, and den/office bonus room! You’ll feel right at home in this charming and inviting space! Make it yours while you can!!
